Kids Toys Review: Star Wars Command Star Destroyer Set.

Create battles and destroy armies with the Command sets! This Star Destroyer set includes a force of 3 obedient Stormtrooper figures and a Darth Vader figure to lead them against anyone who dares to challenge Imperial rule in the remote-controlled Star Destroyer vehicle. With 3 Rebel Soldiers under the command of your exclusive Luke Skywalker figure, will the rebels be able to strike back against the Empire? They'll have to dodge the Energy Blast Balls that the Star Destroyer fires! Take charge and command your battle with the Star Destroyer set! Star Wars products are produced by Hasbro under license from Lucasfilm Ltd. Hasbro and all related terms are trademarks of Hasbro. 

The galaxy is in turmoil. Rebel spaceships are striking out against the evil Galactic Empire and the forces of the dark side. The Empire's sinister agents are intent on flushing out Rebel spies and crushing the Rebellion forever! Will you lead the Rebellion and take on the powerful Imperial armies? Or will you give in to the power of the dark side and impose order on the galaxy by tyranny and force?

Re-create the epic battles of Star Wars! Or create your own new battles by facing off armies of Stormtroopers and Imperial forces against Rebel Soldiers and Lightsaber-wielding Jedi.

Star Wars Command figures and vehicles put the fate of the galaxy in your hands. You're in command! 

Create Battles – Destroy Armies!
Take Charge and Command Your Battle! Jedi Knight Luke Skywalker leads the Rebels in a final assault against the Galactic Empire. Will you wield the power of the dark side and launch your Star Destroyer to crush the rebellion? Or will you embrace your destiny as Luke Skywalker, confront Darth Vader, and bring the Empire to its knees? The Star Wars Command Star Destroyer set includes classic Star Wars characters from Episode VI Return of the Jedi: Luke Skywalker, Darth Vader, 3 Rebel Soldiers, and 3 Stormtroopers!

Use the Force! Remote Control Star Destroyer
Also included is one of the Empire's most powerful weapons: a Star Destroyer! Use the included Command Controller to send the remote-control Star Destroyer racing forward into action! Different hand positions control the Star Destroyer: hand up and the Star Destroyer charges forward. Hand down and the Star Destroyer lunges into reverse while turning! And when you really want to show the Rebels the power of the dark side, turn your hand over. The Star Destroyer will open and fire Energy Blasts to crush the rebellion! Fire 1 Energy Blast at a time or fire all 4 one after the other!

Exclusive Luke Skywalker Figure
This is your chance to get an exclusive Luke Skywalker figure available only in this set! Face off in a climactic battle against Darth Vader and the forces of the dark side! The Rebels have always been outnumbered, and with the Empire unleashing the Star Destroyer, the Rebels are greatly outgunned. You could be their only hope!

Includes:
Luke Skywalker (Exclusive), Darth Vader, 3 Rebel Soldiers, 3 Stormtroopers, Star Destroyer, 4 Energy Blast Balls, and Command Controller.

snippet.title: 2015 McDONALD'S PRIPARA JAPAN SET OF 6 HAPPY MEAL KIDS TOYS TAKARA TOMY TRADING CARDS REVIEW
snippet.description:
Here at Kids Meal Toys we review the 2015 PriPara McDonald's Japan Takara Tomy  A.R.T.S. trading cards. These are from McDonalds Japan happy set happy meal toys in November 2015. PriPara stands for Prism Paradise and it is based on an arcade video game in 2014. In Japanese it is known as プリパラ happy set toys.

The toys for boys running at the same time as the PriPara trading cards are the Dragon Ball Z Heroes trading cards. Dragon Ball Heroes has all our heroes from Dragon Ball and Dragon Ball Z series. There are 6 Bandai McDonald's Dragon Ball trading cards to collect! Dragon Ball Heroes ドラゴンボール ヒーローズ is a Japanese video arcade game developed by Dimps, as the sixth DBZ Dragon Ball Z: Data Carddass game.
